{"tid":1256420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯邦快遞(FedEx)控告美國政府，稱若違反政府禁止承運向中國企業出口的產品，不應負責","createTime":"2019-06-25T04:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T23:52:00.000Z","uid":252013,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d46a75df14cd4b200b0f7394b992cec950bda43","tid":1256420,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"為錢告番自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12:00 聯邦快遞(FedEx)控告美國政府，稱若無意中承運違反政府禁止向某些中國企業出口的產品，公司不應負責。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦快遞上週將一個裝有華為手機寄往美國的包裹退回英國，再次引發中方的不滿，聯邦快遞將此事解釋為操作失誤，不過聯邦快遞仍有可能因此被列入...<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443gy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=dfc7be9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"},{"pid":"84dde2c82fbfdb774b182c95e1523a9fdd0e5b87","tid":1256420,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"正常既<br />\n&ldquo;無意中&rdquo;<br />\n殺人犯坐巴士著草唔通告埋巴士公司咩<br />\n<br />\n睇下個官會點講"},{"pid":"3c7def6cd9a4770f963028c53136bc3062856764","tid":1256420,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84dde2c82fbfdb774b182c95e1523a9fdd0e5b87","tid":1256420,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"正常既<br />\n&ldquo;無意中&rdquo;<br />\n殺人犯坐巴士著草唔通告埋巴士公司咩<br />\n<br />\n睇下個官會點講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"未比人告，先告人......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14d5d1c9b8e48c1ae26b897771d6e19ec616c16","tid":1256420,"uid":133412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"先下手為強。"},{"pid":"5e12b64